00:00:54.600 --> 00:00:55.510
JON: Hello?

00:00:55.510 --> 00:00:57.420
RETO MEIER: Hello, welcome
to the show.

00:00:57.420 --> 00:00:57.940
JON: Thank you.

00:00:57.940 --> 00:00:59.520
Greetings from Norway.

00:00:59.520 --> 00:01:01.010
RETO MEIER: So tell us a little
bit about your app.

00:01:01.010 --> 00:01:02.900
And introduce yourself,
of course, please.

00:01:02.900 --> 00:01:03.370
JON: Yeah.

00:01:03.370 --> 00:01:04.180
My name is Jon.

00:01:04.180 --> 00:01:05.310
I'm from NSB.

00:01:05.310 --> 00:01:07.260
I'm a digital consultant.

00:01:07.260 --> 00:01:11.642
And I'm going to talk
about the NSB

00:01:11.642 --> 00:01:14.500
app, which we submitted.

00:01:14.500 --> 00:01:20.020
It's the 5.0 version, so
