00:20:04.520 --> 00:20:06.630
I had to code it all myself to
try and decide whether it's

00:20:06.630 --> 00:20:12.840
going to use GPS or Wi-Fi to
work out where the phone is.

00:20:12.840 --> 00:20:18.440
Yeah, so the Symbian version had
400,000 registered users.

00:20:18.440 --> 00:20:22.030
The Android version is
a fraction of that.

00:20:22.030 --> 00:20:25.670
Only a few thousands people
have used it, I think.

00:20:25.670 --> 00:20:26.940
So yeah, that's Phonelocator.

