side is your detail.

00:46:36.370 --> 00:46:38.440
So that's one way we
could approach it.

00:46:38.440 --> 00:46:40.940
But definitely for "Android
Design in Action," if we get a

00:46:40.940 --> 00:46:43.510
chance to take a look at this,
we'll see if that pans out.

00:46:43.510 --> 00:46:45.410
It's just kind of an
off-the-cuff idea.

00:46:45.410 --> 00:46:48.880
IAN NI-LEWIS: Yeah, I have to
admit, that's the one thing.

00:46:48.880 --> 00:46:51.290
I feel like every single page
here is beautiful, but the

00:46:51.290 --> 00:46:53.430
navigation is a little weird.

00:46:53.430 --> 00:46:56.250
And right now, I'm just trying
to figure out how to get back

00:46:56.250 --> 00:46:57.500
to the sarcastic cat.

00:47:01.230 --> 00:47:02.690
RETO MEIER: Yeah, it's
definitely a beautiful app.

00:47:02.690 --> 00:47:05.200
I think we really want to
emphasize the fact that it

00:47:05.200 --> 00:47:06.610
looks great.

00:47:06.610 --> 00:47:10.710
Even understanding nothing in
terms of Norwegian, you're

00:47:10.710 --> 00:47:13.540
still able to navigate it and
understand what's going on.

00:47:13.540 --> 00:47:16.800
You've used icons in the right
places to be able to

00:47:16.800 --> 00:47:17.240
understand.

00:47:17.240 --> 00:47:19.840
Like again, here, even without
understanding what these

00:47:19.840 --> 00:47:22.670
categories are, it's obvious to
me that they are categories

00:47:22.670 --> 00:47:25.240
and that I can use them to
navigate into the app.

00:47:25.240 --> 00:47:26.950
And I can figure out
where search is.

00:47:26.950 --> 00:47:29.130
I understand how to
change prices.

00:47:29.130 --> 00:47:32.040
I understand what I'm looking
at, what it represents.

00:47:32.040 --> 00:47:36.320
And it actually represents a
really good example of what we

00:47:36.320 --> 00:47:39.070
should all be doing when we
create our apps, which is

00:47:39.070 --> 00:47:40.550
trying to use it without
being able to

00:47:40.550 --> 00:47:42.770
understand any of the language.

00:47:42.770 --> 00:47:47.780
Even do a localization in just
gibberish, so that the text

00:47:47.780 --> 00:47:50.630
lengths are about the right
size, but you have no idea

00:47:50.630 --> 00:47:51.100
what it says.

00:47:51.100 --> 00:47:52.710
And then give it to someone
and see how well

00:47:52.710 --> 00:47:54.050
they navigate it.

00:47:54.050 --> 00:47:56.870
It gives you a really good idea
of how your visual cues

00:47:56.870 --> 00:47:59.310
are working, how the layout,
